setoid_replace (x || z || y) with (x || y || z).

Lemma includes_Star_monotone : forall x y, x <= y -> (Star x) <= (Star y).

Theorem Star_left : forall r, (Eps || (Star r ++ r)) <= Star r.
Lemma Star_eq_left_s : forall s a b x, (b || (a ++ x)) <= x -> ((Star a) ++ b) ~== s -> x ~== s.

case_eq((Star a ++ b) ~= s); case_eq(x ~= s); intros H1 H2; rewrite matches_Or; rewrite H1; rewrite H2; try reflexivity.

Theorem Star_eq_right_s : forall s a b x, (b || (x ++ a)) <= x -> (b ++ (Star a)) ~== s -> x ~== s.

Theorem Star_eq_right : forall a b x, (b || (x ++ a)) <= x -> (b ++ (Star a)) <= x.
case_eq((b ++ Star a) ~= s); case_eq(x ~= s); intros H1 H2; rewrite matches_Or; rewrite H1; rewrite H2; try reflexivity.
